messageBody:
Hi All,

I thought it could be a good way to learn QuickScript by writing back and forth using nothing but QuickScript. To make this most effective I believe it should be hand written. If anyone wants to start writing by way of regular postal mail, please let me know. Reading someone else's writing should help a lot.

Chuck
chpeckNOSPAM@...

P.S. don't forget to take the NOSPAM out of the email before using it.
